name: LSD Snares Complete
description:
Contains the Original Series and the Signature Series Snares

Original Series:
Lots of mix-ready snare samples, raw as well as heavily processed.
High-end snare drums, recorded in LSD Studios Live Room through top-notch gear (API, Smart Research, SSL, Apogee, Urei).
Processed to fit your mix.
9 Root snares with 5 different types of processing each (45 different snares in the original series).

Signature Series:
These are modelled after a certain style/band

Multiple velocities for each snare (soft, medium, hard and rimshot)

Download Version
